<P>
BERLIN -- Russian Foreign Minister Yevgeny Primakov today
hinted that Moscow was not opposed to NATO enlargement as such,
but could not accept weapons and troops being moved eastward.
</P>
<P>
PARIS -- A new generation Ariane-5 rocket was destructed by
ground controllers about 40 seconds after lifting off today from
Kourou in French Guiana, French television said.
</P>
