Mererani Village, looting and setting ablaze homes in revenge for
the stabbing of a soldier, local reports said today.
</P>
<P>
Hundreds of soldiers invaded Mererani Village, 26 km west of
the northern town of Arusha, on Saturday night and looted and set
ablaze some 15 homes, bars, shops, restaurants and lodging
houses, according to the reports.
</P>
