<HEADLINE> Egyptian, Syrian, Saudi FMs Hold Talks on Israel </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
KUWAIT CITY, June 4 (Xinhua) -- The foreign ministers of Egypt,
Syria and Saudi Arabia resumed their talks today in Saudi capital
Riyadh on post-election Israel, reports reaching here from Riyadh
said.
</P>
<P>
