<HEADLINE> Hong Kong to Hold Floor Products Fair </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, June 4 (Xinhua) -- Hong Kong will hold a large trade
fair in October to show up-to-date products and installation
systems for all types of decorative flooring and carpets.
</P>
<P>
Entitled as Asiaflor '96, the fair will present flooring
products such as rugs, carpets, vinyl, wood, laminate and rubber
flooring, fibers, raw materials, installation equipment and
subfloor products.
</P>
<P>
According to an official of the organizers, the increasing
number of prestigious building projects set to be completed in
Asia over the next five years has led to a significant heightening
of interest in quality products, new installation techniques,
unusual visual appearances and design.
</P>
<P>
He said that Asiaflor will attract flooring professionals,
interior designers, architects and specifiers from throughout the
Asia-Pacific region to meet the world's leading flooring suppliers
for the first time at an Asia-based fair.
</P>
<P>
The show will feature seminar and training sessions and
exhibitors from 25 countries and regions in Europe, America, Asia,
the Middle East and Australia.  
</P>
</TEXT>
