<P>
BANGKOK, June 4 (Xinhua) -- Thai Prime Minister Banharn
Silpa-Archa will lead a grand candle-lit ceremony here on Sunday
night to celebrate the 50th anniversary of King Bhumibol
Adulyadej's ascension to the throne.
