<P>
-- The Central Bureau of Investigation will not drop "hawala"
economic scandal charges against S.R. Bommai who recently joined
the cabinet of the United Front.
</P>
<P>
The Economic Times
</P>
<P>
-- The differences among the United Front constituents over
public sector unit divestment have delayed the finalization of the
United Front's program.  
</P>
