<HEADLINE> Yakovlev Elected St. Petersburg Mayor </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MOSCOW, June 3 (Xinhua) -- Vladimir Yakovlev became mayor of
Russia's second biggest city of St. Petersburg with 47.5 percent
of vote compared to 45.8 percent for Antoly Sobchak in the count
completed after Sunday's second-round run-off.
</P>
<P>
