<P>
JOHANNESBURG, June 3 (Xinhua) -- Wayne Ferreira will spearhead
its Olympic tennis squad as South Africa finalized the roster
recently, the National Olympic Committee of South Africa (NOCSA)
said on Monday.
</P>
<P>
Apart from the singles, Wayne Ferreira will also compete in the
doubles with partner Ellis Ferreira.
</P>
